Package main.gateways.beans

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EventBean
    EventBean is used to serialize and deserialize Event objects into string form Each Event can be represented by one or more EventBeans
    InboxBean
    InboxBean is used to serialize and deserialize Inboxes Each Inbox can be represented by one InboxBean
    MessageBean
    MesssageBean is used to serialize and deserialize Messsages Each Messsage can be represented by one MesssageBean
    RoomBean
    RoomBean is used to serialize and deserialize Rooms Each Room can be represented by one or more RoomBeans
    UserBean
    UserBean is used to serialize and deserialize users
